1
00:01:05,856 --> 00:01:08,288
=No Doubt In Us=
(Adapted from the Manman comic No Doubt in Us)

2
00:01:08,416 --> 00:01:11,328
=Episode 1=

3
00:01:12,832 --> 00:01:15,072
(Chongzheng Hall, Chen Empire)

4
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:30,599
(Xiao Jinyun, Emperor)
Long live the Emperor!

5
00:01:42,240 --> 00:01:43,616
(Xu Yu, Empress)

6
00:01:44,599 --> 00:01:45,760
Mountain-River Cleaver!

7
00:01:55,424 --> 00:01:57,184
(The List of Concubine Candidates)

8
00:01:59,959 --> 00:02:01,120
On borders south and north,

9
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:02,239
beacons rise on all sides.

10
00:02:02,239 --> 00:02:03,280
Plague in the East Sea.

11
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,319
Drought in Liangyuan.

12
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:05,239
Banditry in Lingnan.

13
00:02:05,239 --> 00:02:06,120
The state's in peril.

14
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:10,639
The ministers do not think
of the people and the state.

15
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:12,639
They only care about my harem.

16
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:16,599
What business is it of theirs
how many I marry?

17
00:02:29,879 --> 00:02:31,000
Skyward Thrust!

18
00:02:42,479 --> 00:02:43,400
Xu Yu.

19
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:51,759
Your Majesty.

20
00:02:53,039 --> 00:02:55,039
Why wasn't his arrival announced?

21
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:56,439
Xu Yu,

22
00:02:57,039 --> 00:02:58,319
how dare you

23
00:02:58,599 --> 00:03:00,000
hand over the Empress's Seal!

24
00:03:01,479 --> 00:03:02,840
Isn't that what you wished for?

25
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:05,599
After all, you never truly
wanted me to be Empress.

26
00:03:05,599 --> 00:03:06,112
You...

27
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:11,840
If you're frail, you shouldn't keep
running out to catch a chill.

28
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:13,400
So according to you,

29
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:14,960
I am a burden to you.

30
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:16,159
Good.

31
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:18,360
Since you lead such a leisurely life,

32
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,759
I'll give you something to do.

33
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,240
Eunuch Qin.

34
00:03:27,039 --> 00:03:28,639
Draft the list of concubine candidates.

35
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:33,400
Alright. It's not like
I haven't done it before.

36
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:36,960
As long as Your Majesty
trusts my judgment.

37
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:41,280
Choose me!

38
00:03:41,408 --> 00:03:43,599
Choose me, Your Majesty!

39
00:03:43,599 --> 00:03:44,400
Your Majesty!

40
00:03:45,039 --> 00:03:45,840
Choose me!

41
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:46,680
Your Majesty!

42
00:03:48,039 --> 00:03:49,120
Choose me!

43
00:03:49,199 --> 00:03:50,400
Your Majesty, look at me!

44
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,199
Your Majesty!

45
00:03:53,879 --> 00:03:56,719
The eight concubine candidates
are all talented and virtuous.

46
00:03:56,719 --> 00:03:58,120
They'd never lead you astray.

47
00:03:58,120 --> 00:03:59,759
If you do not indulge in women,

48
00:03:59,759 --> 00:04:01,639
it'll be more beneficial for the court.

49
00:04:02,319 --> 00:04:04,120
I think it's unnecessary.

50
00:04:05,599 --> 00:04:06,560
Your Majesty!

51
00:04:10,639 --> 00:04:11,240
No need.

52
00:04:12,039 --> 00:04:13,152
With your judgment,

53
00:04:13,152 --> 00:04:15,280
you'll make a mockery
of the concubine selection.

54
00:04:15,479 --> 00:04:18,240
Your harem is filled
with countless beauties.

55
00:04:18,439 --> 00:04:19,920
How many more do you need?

56
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:22,560
The concubine selection
is for the balance of the court.

57
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:25,680
Since when does Chen Empire need women
in the harem to stabilize the court?

58
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:26,600
Xu Yu.

59
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:27,839
Enough.

60
00:04:28,279 --> 00:04:30,199
Whatever I do is wrong anyway.

61
00:04:30,199 --> 00:04:32,399
No matter what I do,
Your Majesty will never trust me.

62
00:04:32,399 --> 00:04:34,759
Then simply let Consort Zhao
manage the harem.

63
00:04:34,759 --> 00:04:36,680
So I'm not in the way
of you producing heirs.

64
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,560
Do you really not care?

65
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:39,439
I don't care.

66
00:04:39,439 --> 00:04:40,079
Fine.

67
00:04:40,839 --> 00:04:41,560
Pass the order.

68
00:04:41,959 --> 00:04:44,759
Consort Zhao will take
the Empress's Seal and run the harem.

69
00:04:44,896 --> 00:04:45,480
Yes.

70
00:04:51,968 --> 00:04:52,639
You...

71
00:04:59,808 --> 00:05:00,352
I...

72
00:05:05,959 --> 00:05:07,519
The Empress's Seal

73
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:10,040
(Zhao Qiluo)
matches my attire best.

74
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:10,959
Exactly.

75
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:12,360
In my opinion,

76
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:13,879
the Empress's Seal in your hands

77
00:05:13,879 --> 00:05:16,399
(Beauty Liang)
is brighter than in the Empress's hands.

78
00:05:16,519 --> 00:05:18,279
Now that the seal is in your hands,

79
00:05:18,279 --> 00:05:20,639
(Lady Tao)
even the palace seems brighter.

80
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:22,199
The Empress's Seal

81
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:25,879
should be held by someone
capable and dignified.

82
00:05:26,319 --> 00:05:27,072
Look.

83
00:05:27,072 --> 00:05:29,480
I can even tolerate that belly of yours.

84
00:05:29,959 --> 00:05:31,879
Consort Zhao, you're right.

85
00:05:35,279 --> 00:05:36,959
Merely transferring the seal

86
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:39,959
does not demonstrate your ability
to manage the harem.

87
00:05:40,319 --> 00:05:41,839
I have over 100 account books here.

88
00:05:41,839 --> 00:05:43,079
I cannot manage them all.

89
00:05:43,079 --> 00:05:45,560
But I believe you can.

90
00:05:47,639 --> 00:05:48,720
Your Majesty,

91
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:51,040
you are deliberately
making things difficult for me.

92
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:52,639
Unless

93
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:55,319
you can't read the account books?

94
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:57,199
Then the seal...

95
00:05:57,199 --> 00:05:58,800
Who said Her Highness can't?

96
00:05:59,160 --> 00:06:02,160
She's intelligent
and exceedingly learned.

97
00:06:02,279 --> 00:06:04,720
Managing these account books
is effortless for her.

98
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:06,272
Not to mention a hundred.

99
00:06:06,272 --> 00:06:10,199
Even if it's a thousand,
Her Highness can handle them with ease.

100
00:06:10,368 --> 00:06:11,959
Right, Your Highness?

101
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:15,920
If you don't know
how to speak, then don't.

102
00:06:17,839 --> 00:06:19,040
Of course.

103
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:20,600
- I...
- I'm done on my part.

104
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:21,639
I'll take my leave.

105
00:06:22,336 --> 00:06:22,959
Wait.

106
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:25,639
Now the Empress's Seal is in my hands.

107
00:06:25,639 --> 00:06:27,319
I have authority over the harem.

108
00:06:27,759 --> 00:06:31,199
It is against the rules for you
to carry a sword in the palace.

109
00:06:31,519 --> 00:06:32,079
Someone!

110
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,480
Disarm her sword immediately.

111
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,072
- Yes.
- Yes.

112
00:06:36,519 --> 00:06:37,680
Your Majesty!

113
00:06:37,959 --> 00:06:39,199
Why such panic?

114
00:06:39,279 --> 00:06:42,199
Her Majesty and Consort Zhao
are quarreling again.

115
00:06:42,199 --> 00:06:44,480
I heard Her Majesty even drew her sword.

116
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:46,199
You want my sword?

117
00:06:46,199 --> 00:06:48,000
You'll have to defeat me first.

118
00:06:49,824 --> 00:06:50,439
Xu Yu.

119
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:54,319
Your Majesty.

120
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,199
Your Majesty.

121
00:06:56,839 --> 00:06:58,439
Her Majesty wants to kill me.

122
00:06:59,079 --> 00:07:00,600
Please help me.

123
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:01,360
Xu Yu,

124
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:02,920
come with me.

125
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:06,800
Your Majesty.

126
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:08,639
You're out of favor again.

127
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:11,720
But I'm still the Empress.

128
00:07:11,839 --> 00:07:12,920
You enjoy exclusive favor,

129
00:07:13,199 --> 00:07:15,519
yet where's the heir
to ease His Majesty's worries?

130
00:07:22,519 --> 00:07:23,439
Xu Yu,

131
00:07:24,439 --> 00:07:26,120
you're just a general's daughter.

132
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:28,079
My father is the Grand Chancellor.

133
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,480
Why should I fear you?

134
00:07:32,199 --> 00:07:32,759
Xu Yu.

135
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,959
Should Your Majesty reprimand me,

136
00:07:38,959 --> 00:07:39,920
just say it outright.

137
00:07:40,319 --> 00:07:42,319
After all, you scold me indiscriminately

138
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:43,839
time and again.

139
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:45,560
Court factions are imbalanced.

140
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:48,639
Grand Chancellor Zhao,
the top civil official, holds sway.

141
00:07:48,639 --> 00:07:50,120
If you harm Zhao Qiluo now,

142
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:51,959
I...

143
00:07:54,519 --> 00:07:57,000
(I can hardly guarantee your safety.)

144
00:07:58,120 --> 00:07:59,680
You'd feel heartbroken.

145
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:01,680
I understand.

146
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:04,759
Your sword-carved wooden head

147
00:08:04,759 --> 00:08:05,800
could never understand.

148
00:08:06,399 --> 00:08:07,560
Shame on you as Empress.

149
00:08:09,079 --> 00:08:10,639
Then I dare ask Your Majesty.

150
00:08:11,199 --> 00:08:12,800
Do I look like the Empress to you now?

151
00:08:14,319 --> 00:08:15,279
What do you mean?

152
00:08:15,759 --> 00:08:16,920
Every time you visit me,

153
00:08:17,199 --> 00:08:20,560
you either scold me for others' sake
or reprimand me over palace affairs.

154
00:08:20,759 --> 00:08:21,839
How do others view me?

155
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:23,759
Have you considered my feelings?

156
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:25,000
So you mean

157
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:28,360
you resent my entrusting
the Empress's Seal to Consort Zhao?

158
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:31,399
Have you ever devoted
half that sword-swinging passion

159
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:33,159
to managing the imperial harem?

160
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:36,360
Then just strip me of my title
and cast me out of the palace

161
00:08:36,759 --> 00:08:37,960
to make way for Zhao Qiluo.

162
00:08:40,559 --> 00:08:41,320
Xu Yu,

163
00:08:41,679 --> 00:08:43,080
do you wish to leave me so badly?

164
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:44,519
Isn't this exactly what you want?

165
00:08:44,519 --> 00:08:45,080
Xu Yu!

166
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:48,288
Get away.

167
00:08:52,279 --> 00:08:53,039
Xiao Jinyun!

168
00:09:23,120 --> 00:09:24,080
Someone! Help!

169
00:09:24,160 --> 00:09:26,080
(Fengyi Palace)
Their Majesties fell into the water!

170
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:39,080
Why am I in Fengyi Palace?

171
00:09:51,039 --> 00:09:53,360
(This is Xiao Jinyun's study?)

172
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:07,519
(I've actually become Xiao Jinyun?)

173
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:41,399
Why is this growing here?

174
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:44,720
Your Majesty.

175
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:47,399
Your Majesty.

176
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:50,080
I heard Her Majesty
pushed you into the water.

177
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:52,159
I was so worried.

178
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:53,600
Stay away from me.

179
00:10:54,519 --> 00:10:56,879
Please let me check if you're hurt.

180
00:10:57,440 --> 00:10:59,399
D-Don't touch me.

181
00:11:00,320 --> 00:11:01,000
Your Majesty.

182
00:11:01,050 --> 00:11:03,120
(Empress Dowager)
Shall we summon Physician Jiang again?

183
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:04,519
No.

184
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:07,240
Your Majesty,

185
00:11:07,639 --> 00:11:08,879
what's wrong?

186
00:11:09,159 --> 00:11:10,639
I'm Qiluo.

187
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:12,919
Don't you adore me most?

188
00:11:15,159 --> 00:11:17,879
His Majesty seems too traumatized

189
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:21,200
to recognize me.

190
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:22,799
Your Majesty.

191
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:24,200
His Majesty is shocked.

192
00:11:24,559 --> 00:11:26,080
He should rest properly.

193
00:11:26,919 --> 00:11:28,559
I'll confront Xu Yu.

194
00:11:29,360 --> 00:11:30,240
You go.

195
00:11:31,879 --> 00:11:32,480
I'll go too.

196
00:11:33,039 --> 00:11:33,919
You go as well.

197
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:36,320
(They're going to confront me?)

198
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:37,840
(Wait.)

199
00:11:38,559 --> 00:11:40,159
(I've become Xiao Jinyun.)

200
00:11:40,639 --> 00:11:42,200
(Then doesn't that mean Xiao Jinyun)

201
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:43,519
(is me?)

202
00:12:07,904 --> 00:12:13,088
♪Parting clouds
to pluck the waxing moon♪

203
00:12:13,824 --> 00:12:18,387
♪Brewing a pot of bygone years♪

204
00:12:19,712 --> 00:12:25,127
♪Chill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul♪

205
00:12:25,696 --> 00:12:30,240
♪Drunk through lifetimes
with no dreams returned♪

206
00:12:30,880 --> 00:12:36,144
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

207
00:12:36,512 --> 00:12:42,189
♪Returning to drift
through the mortal world♪

208
00:12:42,528 --> 00:12:44,544
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

209
00:12:44,736 --> 00:12:48,480
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

210
00:12:49,056 --> 00:12:53,728
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

211
00:12:54,272 --> 00:12:56,032
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

212
00:12:56,352 --> 00:12:59,968
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

213
00:13:00,215 --> 00:13:05,742
♪Tell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more♪
